{"tid":1849770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】四季酒店大堂武漢男女不適 急送瑪麗醫院隔離治療","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T13:19:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":60,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"b6370272f852cb25a97f3dc670022eda6c1b20ca","tid":1849770,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ygmfl4A5RZ-9iIbPBXV5ZksViRA=/414x232/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/HXVMTRFVA4V7AKZYWI5P4FXTCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fygmfl4A5RZ-9iIbPBXV5ZksViRA%3D%2F414x232%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FHXVMTRFVA4V7AKZYWI5P4FXTCM.jpg&h=5fdc03d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎陰霾擴散至香港的五星級酒店？昨晚（28日）11時18分，消防處接報中環金融街8號四季酒店地下大堂，有一對來自內地武漢的中年男女遊客感覺不適，須召喚救護車，兩武漢男女隨即由穿着全副防護衣物的救護員送往瑪麗醫院治療。消息稱，由於兩送院男女來自武漢，性質敏感，兩人將要接受隔離及武漢病毒快速測試，料短期內會有結果。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，四季酒店今午有多名員工在酒店的大門以及地下大堂清潔，包括拖地、以抹布清潔玻璃大門、梳化、牆壁等等，清洗得相當仔細。記者亦見到不少穿西裝的酒店職員疑似在督促清潔行動，但未見有貼出告知提醒住客小心任何傳染病。<br />\n<br />\n記者曾訪問部份四季酒店的住客，他們大都對昨晚的風波並不知情。丹麥遊客Aslam（左）和Eva今晨才check in四季酒店，他們都不知道酒店大堂內曾有武漢男女疑因不適送院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200129/large/1580282602_960c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200129%2Flarge%2F1580282602_960c.jpg&h=ee6251de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/A5HMKEONI7GO72YIUXECTTNGY4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FA5HMKEONI7GO72YIUXECTTNGY4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=99a61721\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FA5HMKEONI7GO72YIUXECTTNGY4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=bdb1dd6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/A5HMKEONI7GO72YIUXECTTNGY4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6884b5d38f6c412fa1be0d5631d65f343ba1a52d","tid":1849770,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjrMrcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjrMrcp.jpg&h=e20e71f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d0d86a88b4bf4689ba66a93ef61a65a5731d9246","tid":1849770,"uid":77196,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"五星級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fabcf07d0d2a8248a7e6bcd63a21147c49353c","tid":1849770,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0d86a88b4bf4689ba66a93ef61a65a5731d9246","tid":1849770,"uid":77196,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"五星級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:25:43.